title: Theme Showcase
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Mermaid supports five built-in themes. The same diagram is shown below in each theme for comparison. Pass the theme via the `theme` attribute on the `<$mermaid>` widget.

```
<$mermaid theme="forest" text='
flowchart LR
    A --> B --> C
'></$mermaid>
```

---

!! default

<$mermaid theme="default" text='
flowchart LR
    User["User"] --> Auth["Auth Service"]
    Auth --> DB[("Database")]
    Auth --> Cache[("Cache")]
    Auth -->|fail| Error["Error Handler"]
'></$mermaid>

