!! Git graph themes

Git graphs have their own per-diagram theme support and additional theme customization. See [[Gitgraph Base Theme]], [[Gitgraph Dark Theme]], [[Gitgraph Forest Theme]], [[Gitgraph Neutral Theme]], and [[Gitgraph Default Theme]] for examples.

